The children's oath in the poem is the refrain **"Mera watan wohi hai, mera watan wohi hai"** (میرا وطن وہی ہے، میرا وطن وہی ہے) — "This is my homeland, this is my homeland" — repeated after each of the four stanzas that recount India's historical and spiritual greatness.
